/www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/cate-blanchett-fleetwood-mac@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/cate-blanchett-fleetwood-mac@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/cate-blanchett-fleetwood-mac@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/cate-blanchett-fleetwood-mac@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/cate-blanchett-fleetwood-mac@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/cate-blanchett">凯特·布兰切特</a>透露，她的新政治喜剧电影<em>《谣言》</em>是以影响深远的<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/fleetwood-mac">弗利特伍德麦克</a>专辑命名的。</p><ul class="post-content-read-more"><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/features/music-interviews/stevie-nicks-in-fleetwood-mac-christine-mcvie-and-i-were-a-force-of-nature-2785710">史蒂夫·尼克斯：“在弗利特伍德麦克，克里斯汀·麦克维和我是一股自然的力量”</a></strong></li></ul><p>周日（5 月 19 日）布兰切特在出席戛纳电影节新闻发布会时，公开了这部电影及其片名。前一天晚上（5 月 18 日）首映后，布兰切特获得了长达四分钟的起立鼓掌，布兰切特表示，这部电影是以 Fleetwood Mac 1977 年著名专辑命名的。</p><p>布兰切特在接受<a href="https://variety.com/2024/film/news/cate-blanchett-rumours-named-after-fleetwood-mac-album-1236009146/" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>《综艺》采访</em></a>时表示：“昨晚我确实与[导演]盖伦[约翰逊]确认了一件事，但很奇怪的是，排练时从未出现过这个问题，那就是：‘这部电影到底为什么叫<em>《谣言</em>》？’”我丈夫说，“那是在 Fleetwood Mac 专辑之后吗？”你说，‘是的，是的。’” </p><figure id="attachment_3522167" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3522167" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3522167" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Cate-Blanchett@2000x1270.jpg" alt="凯特·布兰切特 2023" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Cate-Blanchett@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Cate-Blanchett@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Cate-Blanchett@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Cate-Blanchett@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Cate-Blanchett@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Cate-Blanchett@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3522167" class="wp-caption-text"> 2023 年的凯特·布兰切特。图片来源：Edward Berthelot/Getty Images</figcaption></figure><p>影片讲述了一群政客齐聚G7峰会，肩负制定集体声明的任务，却陷入了灯红酒绿和爱情纠葛的故事。</p><p>盖伦·约翰逊接着解释道：“《谣言》这张专辑以充满创意而闻名，每个人都在互相睡觉，所以这对我们来说是有道理的。没有人质疑这一点。我们认为人们、生产者和金融家会说，“为什么<em>有谣言</em>？”但没有人质疑它，所以它就成了标题。”</p><p> <em>《传闻》的</em>主演还包括艾丽西亚·维坎德、查尔斯·丹斯、平武宏和兹拉科·布里奇等。 <em>《谣言》</em>的发行日期尚未公布。 </p><figure id="attachment_3508192" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3508192" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3508192" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/fleetwood-mac-stevie-nicks-christine-mcvie-reunion.jpg" alt="摇滚乐队“Fleetwood Mac”的 Lindsey Buckingham、Christine McVie、Mick Fleetwood、Stevie Nicks 和 John McVie" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/fleetwood-mac-stevie-nicks-christine-mcvie-reunion.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/fleetwood-mac-stevie-nicks-christine-mcvie-reunion-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/fleetwood-mac-stevie-nicks-christine-mcvie-reunion-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/fleetwood-mac-stevie-nicks-christine-mcvie-reunion-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/fleetwood-mac-stevie-nicks-christine-mcvie-reunion-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/fleetwood-mac-stevie-nicks-christine-mcvie-reunion-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3508192" class="wp-caption-text"> 1977 年左右：（LR）摇滚乐队“Fleetwood Mac”的 Lindsey Buckingham、Christine McVie、Mick Fleetwood、Stevie Nicks 和 John McVie 在 1977 年左右摆出姿势拍照（图片来源：Michael Ochs Archives/Getty Images）</figcaption></figure><p>本月早些时候，据透露<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/fleetwood-macs-rumours-named-as-the-best-selling-vinyl-of-70s-80s-and-90s-3752936">Fleetwood Mac 的《Rumours》被评为 70 年代、80 年代和 90 年代最畅销的黑胶唱片</a>。据透露，Fleetwood Mac 还于 4 月份<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/oasis-wonderwall-named-uks-most-streamed-song-from-70s-80s-and-90s-3612267">跻身英国 70 年代、80 年代和 90 年代流媒体播放量最高的歌曲之列</a>。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/cate-blanchett-film-rumours-was-named-after-fleetwood-mac-album-3757600">凯特·布兰切特 (Cate Blanchett) 的新政治喜剧电影《谣言》(Rumours) 以弗利特伍德麦克 (Fleetwood Mac) 专辑</a>首次在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上亮相而命名。</p> ;
尼尔·杨 (Neil Young) 与疯马 (Crazy Horse) 宣布推出新档案专辑《Early Daze》 https://www.nme.com/news/music/neil-young-crazy-horse-announce-new-archival-album-early-daze-3757595?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=neil-young-crazy-horse-宣布新档案专辑早期发呆Surej SinghMon, 20 May 2024 02:43:30 +0000 Music NewsNewsFolkRockhttps://www.nme.com/?p=3757595 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/neil-young-crazy-horse@2000x1270.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="1978 年，尼尔·杨 (Neil Young) 与疯马乐队 (Crazy Horse) 一起表演" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/neil-young-crazy-horse@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/neil-young-crazy-horse@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/neil-young-crazy-horse@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/neil-young-crazy-horse@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/neil-young-crazy-horse@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/neil-young-crazy-horse@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>这张专辑包含最初录制于 1969 年的歌曲，将于 6 月下旬发行</p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/neil-young-crazy-horse-announce-new-archival-album-early-daze-3757595">Neil Young 和 Crazy Horse 宣布新专辑《Early Daze》</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/neil-young-crazy-horse@2000x1270.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="1978 年，尼尔·杨 (Neil Young) 与疯马乐队 (Crazy Horse) 一起表演" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/neil-young-crazy-horse@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/neil-young-crazy-horse@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/neil-young-crazy-horse@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/neil-young-crazy-horse@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/neil-young-crazy-horse@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/neil-young-crazy-horse@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/neil-young-and-crazy-horse">尼尔·杨 (Neil Young) 和疯马 (Crazy Horse)</a>宣布即将推出一张存档专辑《Early Daze》。</p><ul class="post-content-read-more"><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/neil-young-crazy-horse-barn-review-3114106">Neil Young 和 Crazy Horse – 《谷仓》评论：粗犷的乡村之美，带着希望的感觉</a></strong></li></ul><p>上周末， <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/neil-young">Neil Young</a>在他的<a href="https://neilyoungarchives.com/news/1/article?id=EARLY%20DAZE" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Neil Young Archives 网站</a>上宣布了即将发行的唱片，该唱片是 1969 年与 Crazy Horse 录制的。该专辑将于 6 月 28 日通过 Reprise Records 发售，<a href="https://neilyoung.warnerrecords.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">现已开放预订</a>。</p><p>根据 Neil Young Archives 的说法，“Early Daze”“展示了乐队在 20 世纪 60 年代末的独特风格，捕捉了他们现场表演的精髓以及他们对摇滚乐发展的贡献。”</p><p> 《Early Daze》将包含 10 首歌曲，其中包括来自 Crazy Horse 早期阵容的六首未发行的歌曲，其中包括吉他手 Danny Whitten、鼓手 Ralph Molina、贝斯手 Billy Talbot、键盘手 Jack Nitzsche 和 Young。</p><p> 《Everbody&#39;s Alone》、《Cinnamon Girl》和《Birds》等歌曲将以不同的混音形式发行。 </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/p/C7E8SecpEkw/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);"><div style="padding:16px;"><div style="background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 50%; flex-grow: 0; height: 40px; margin-right: 14px